title: Natural Ecotienda
description: Health food and esoteric store underneath Beep Computer Shop (down the street steps on the left). Offers a big selection of organic dried and chilled vegetarian goods. Variety of tofu, seitan, pates, organic fruit and veggies and milk alternatives. Sells supplements, herbal remedies, loose herbs, cosmetics, natural hair dyes, organic cleaning and laundry products and a macrobiotic section. Holds seminars every Friday at 8pm, including Reiki, Bach Flower remedies, life coaching and yoga, meditation, tarot readings and personalized diet guidance. Spiritual art, music, jewelery, incense, candles, books and precious stones. Welcoming atmosphere.
